.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-2::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, broccoli, cherry, spinach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, march, august
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, indian, american
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, writer, architect, teacher
 1. the architect is the person eating broccoli##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the teacher##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 5. the teacher is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is between the mexican and the person eating artichoke##2
 7. the mexican is on the right of the architect##1
 8. the american is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the canadian##1
10. the entrepreneur is the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person eating cherry is in an odd position##4
12. the mexican is not the architect##6
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the mexican##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food          | cherry    | artichoke | broccoli | spinach       |
| Hobby         | august | january   | july  | march       |
| Music-Genre   | american      | canadian   | indian     | mexican         |
| Sport         | entrepreneur   | writer   | architect | teacher |

