.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, cain, montecristo, havana
4 different games are played: billiard, chess, mah-jongg, go
There 4 different types of food: lime, pear, watermelon, asparagus
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, skateboard
 1. the person eating lime is not the person playing go##6
 2. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 4. the person playing go is not the cain-smoker##6
 5. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 8. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating pear##1
13. the person driving the bike is not the person playing billiard##6
14. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | montecristo   | cain      | havana   | prince |
| Nationality   | mah-jongg | chess  | go | billiard     |
| Pet           | asparagus     | pear | watermelon    | lime    |
| Transport     | skateboard | car        | bike    | ship        |

