 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 8. the aristoff-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the dutch##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is the dutch##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person playing go is not the brazilian##6

