City: edinburgh, liverpool, san-francisco, venice
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
 3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
 4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 6. the person who growspoppy is the manager##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the scooter##1
10. the fisherman is the person traveling to venice##1
11. the police-officer is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
12. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |    4    |
