11. the british is the british##1
12. the british is between the person eating peach and the person traveling to london##2
13. the person traveling to london is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | colone | london     | paris    | liverpool |
| Music-Genre   | australian | turkish       | british | brazilian    |
| Pet           | goat    | chinchilla | mouse      | guinea-pig |
| Transport     | pumpkin     | raspberry     | plum     | peach |

