.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, sports, horror, epic
House: cottage, palace, cape-cod, townhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, fishing, sudoku
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the cottage house##2
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
 6. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is not the cape-cod house##6
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the townhouse house##1
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

