 3. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 5. the russian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 6. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
 9. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the argentine is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
11. the person who likes blood-red is the person playing domino##1
12. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
14. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

