.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby, skiing, golf
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, 7up, water
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, malaysian, thai
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, june, february
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the american##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 4. the american is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the malaysian is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
11. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | golf | rugby  | skiing     | volleyball     |
| Movie-Genre   | 7up   | juice      | iced-tea   | water     |
| Nationality   | canadian  | american   | malaysian  | thai       |
| Transport     | january   | march | june | february |

 